wikipedia_page.main: Wayne Allen Reittie (born 1988) is a Jamaica international rugby league footballer who plays as a winger for Hunslet R.L.F.C. in the RFL League 1.He has previously played for Doncaster in 2008 National League Two and the 2009 RFL Championship, and the Hunslet Hawks and the York City Knights in Championship 1. Reittie has also played for the Batley Bulldogs and Halifax in the Championship.
